OL,3,CNottingham City Council stops all but
OL,4,Cessential spending after effectively
OL,5,Cdeclaring itself bankrupt
OL,7,FNottingham City Council has
OL,8,Feffectively declared itself bankrupt
OL,9,Fafter issuing a Section114 notice.
OL,11,FThe authority will halt all spending
OL,12,Fother than services it must provide
OL,13,Fby law after it was unable to deliver
OL,14,Fa balanced budget for this year,
OL,15,Fwhich is a legal requirement.
OL,17,FIt follows Birmingham City Council
OL,18,Fwhich issued an S114 notice in
OL,19,FSeptember after admitting that it
OL,20,Fcould not manage its catastrophic
OL,21,Ffinancial crisis without help.
